%section
  %h4 Custom Functions
  %dl.ms-expr-guide-fn-list
    %dt
      %code STR(value)
    %dd
      Convert any value to its string representation.
      %br
      %code STR(42)
      →
      %code '42'
    %dt
      %code DIG(json_string, key1, key2, ...)
    %dd
      Navigate into a JSON string. Returns nil when the path doesn't exist.
      %br
      %code DIG(data, 'user', 'name')
      →
      %code 'Alice'

%section
  %h4 Common Patterns
  %table.ms-expr-guide-tbl
    %tr
      %td
        %code score > 0.8
      %td Threshold check
    %tr
      %td
        %code status = 'active' AND score >= 5
      %td Combined condition
    %tr
      %td
        %code IF(count > 0, total / count, 0)
      %td Safe division
    %tr
      %td
        %code CONTAINS('error', message)
      %td Keyword search
    %tr
      %td
        %code DIG(response, 'choices', '0', 'text')
      %td Deep JSON access
    %tr
      %td
        %code ROUND(price * 1.2, 2)
      %td Math + rounding
    %tr
      %td
        %code NOT(CONTAINS('skip', tags))
      %td Negated search

%section
  %h4 Important Rules
  %ul
    %li
      Strings inside expressions are always
      %strong single-quoted:
      %code name = 'Alice'
    %li
      %code {{var}}
      interpolation happens
      %strong before
      expression evaluation.
    %li
      Unknown variables evaluate to
      %code nil.
    %li
      Division by zero returns
      %code nil
      (no error).
